Key Features of QEDIT
     __________________________________________________________________

Standard Compliant Cryptography

   Future-proof your blockchain with a privacy solution that adheres to
   specifications defined by ZKProof.org.

Controlled Transparency

   Use permissioned auditing tools and stay compliant with GDPR, CCPA, and
   other local data privacy regulations.

Enterprise-Grade Privacy

   Maintain high availability and performance with a robust,
   production-ready solution.

High-Level API & Native Client SDKs

   Leave the cryptography to us, and stay focused on your company’s
   application layer, business logic and user experience.

Blockchain-Agnostic

   Give your team optimal flexibility in choosing the stack that’s most
   suitable for your use case.

Scalable Technology

   Generate ZKPs using proprietary Proof Chaining technology that keeps
   pace with your transaction volume.

Privacy-Preserving Solutions for Enterprise

   QEDIT’s asset transfer solution is designed for large enterprises and
   private consortia operating in a range of vertical industries.

Finance

     * Private or public asset issuance
     * Atomic Swap support for fungible and non-fungible assets
     * Auditing capabilities for regulatory compliance

Supply Chain

     * Optimal collaboration without compromising privacy
     * Unlimited tokenized asset types
     * Proof of provenance to prevent fraud

Insurance

     * Tokenized asset issuance for claims management
     * Multi-claim fraud prevention
     * Privacy-preserving credit and risk scoring

Learn How QEDIT Can Bring Privacy to Your Enterprise Blockchain Application

