About Us
     __________________________________________________________________

   Founded by a world-class team of seasoned entrepreneurs, researchers
   and developers, QEDIT leverages zero-knowledge proof (ZKP) cryptography
   for enterprise blockchains to enable collaboration among competitors.
   QEDIT’s technology safeguards sensitive business data in a
   shared-ledger environment and facilitates companies’ compliance with
   local data privacy regulations.

   QEDIT’s Scientific Advisory Board includes Professor Shafi Goldwasser,
   co-inventor of ZKPs and recipient of the Turing Award, and Professor
   Eran Tromer, a world-renowned expert in ZKP systems and zkSNARKs.

   To drive ZKP adoption, QEDIT helped launch ZKProof.org, an open
   academic initiative for ZKP standardization. The organization hosts
   annual conferences for top-tier cryptographers and practitioners from
   around the world and is supported by industry leaders and
   standardization bodies like the National Institute of Standards and
   Technology (NIST).

