SUPPORT FOR CRYPTOGRAPHIC INDUSTRY STANDARDS

   QEDIT is a founding member and an active contributor to the open
   industry ZKProof.org standardization effort. Our zero-knowledge privacy
   solution adheres to the specifications defined in the ZKProof Community
   Reference Document.

