About

   Founded by a world class team, QEDIT has developed the Zero-Knowledge
   Blockchain. Combining two advanced technologies, zero-knowledge proof
   cryptography and enterprise blockchain, ZK Blockchain solves the
   coordination between actors in the same industry, eliminating the
   necessity of sharing their confidential data. In practice,
   Zero-Knowledge Blockchain provides proof for all parties, without
   disclosing their underlying confidential data

